{"tid":2419782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我打到比人 人地打唔到比我 可以點搞","createTime":"2021-02-23T13:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T13:36:06.000Z","uid":96536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09ea637d730d538b23bde56f18cbf7907cbfef55","tid":2419782,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VE4ZqjP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVE4ZqjP.png&h=5f9680d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日約咗個朋友出街<br />\n佢打咗好多次比我都唔通 以為我收唔到<br />\n但係我又收到佢喺whatsapp同signal搵我<br />\n見到面嘅時候先發現原來我上年封鎖咗佢之後一直都冇解鎖返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到我頭先解鎖返之後 佢打多幾次比我都係打唔通<br />\n連face time都係搵唔到我<br />\n<br />\n但係whatsapp, signal同i message都可以搵到我<br />\n想問下可以點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1932e2fd14aaa7f1c803294782f4467672a0a0","tid":2419782,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:16:53.000Z","msg":"喺手機台開唔到po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f01f421fe885c0bc5d71416368b95339a666069","tid":2419782,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e6a6a5b52972b2f252b4271270aac4e6304466f","tid":2419782,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"330f2b80cda19e3acafeb601b8359579f86e30c6","tid":2419782,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"